Segitség képpen az alábbi mutatja hogy mire gondolok.


SELECT ca.b2_type,
       ca.collateral_type,
       ca.SUBTYPE_OF_REAL_ESTATE_CODE,
       ct.TYPE_OF_REAL_ESTATE_CODE,
       ct.COLLATERAL_CODE,
       cd.TYPE_OF_REAL_ESTATE_CODE,
       cd.COLLATERAL_CODE
from dm_core.CDD_COLLATERAL_ATTRIBUTE ca
left JOIN DM_CORE.CDP_COLLATERAL_TYPES ct
ON ct.COLLATERAL_TYPE=ca.COLLATERAL_TYPE
and ct.ACTIVE_FLAG IN ('Y', 'N')
AND '2019-08-30' BETWEEN ct.VALID_FROM AND ct.VALID_TO
left JOIN DM_CORE.CDP_DSI_COLLATERAL_TYPE_MAPPING cd ON cd.DSI_CODE = ca.SUBTYPE_OF_REAL_ESTATE_CODE
and cd.ACTIVE_FLAG IN ('Y','N')
AND '2019-08-30' BETWEEN cd.VALID_FROM AND cd.VALID_TO
where ca.ACTIVE_FLAG IN ('Y', 'N')
AND '2019-08-30' BETWEEN ca.VALID_FROM AND ca.VALID_TO
and ca.COLLATERAL_CODE = ''
AND ca.B2_TYPE = 'EIG'
AND HITREG_REPORTABLE_FLAG = 'Y'
